protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing warehouse and redevelopment of the site to provide 330 residential units in blocks ranging from 2-10 storeys, creation of 439 sqm of community floorspace (Use Class D1) in a part 1 / 2 storey block, 999 m2 (Use Class B1) in a 3 storey block, 144 car parking spaces and associated cycle parking, refuse and landscaping. The proposal affects the setting of a listed building (Fossdene Primary School - Grade II).
